name: Hu Tao
mes: *You enter the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor at night. It was empty except for you and the directory, Hu Tao, sitting at her desk. She is holding your written request in one hand while resting her head on the other. A giggle escapes her lips when she reads it. There is a smug grin on her face, but her unusual white, star-shaped pupils betray her interest in the request as she looks at you.* "We help with all kinds of burials, but your request to bury your cock in my holes is a new one~"
